{"tid":901971,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"我在大家樂打一人邊爐","createTime":"2018-11-14T12:36:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T15:53:04.000Z","uid":68904,"like":3,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"07635d18a5d09c82eeb089cf38809a384ed6ac02","tid":901971,"uid":68904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T12:36:32.000Z","msg":"即棄用品如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hwJLwd8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhwJLwd8.png&h=1514853d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本身有黑色可重洗膠兜 但又要外加即棄膠兜<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kc30kdC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKc30kdC.png&h=51dc8383&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y30NKFJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy30NKFJ.png&h=35312d30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但大家樂都好環保：<br />\n大家樂發言人表示，現時正實施不同措施「減塑」，預料可令即棄塑膠用量減半。全線分店亦自上月起，用木棒全面代替用於熱飲的膠棒及膠匙。自助點餐機及手機訂餐程式提供「自攜餐盒」、「自攜杯」及「走飲管」的選項。外賣餐具包無加入膠刀，並正研究將膠叉及膠羹改成二合一設計。<br />\n<br />\n發言人指集團正實行不同方案，尋找符合食物安全衛生又不會衍生其他環保問題的替代物料，長遠盼達到不用即棄塑膠餐具目標，當中有19間未能循環再用的餐具，現在研究方法改善。分店現時亦參與海洋公園保育基金的「無飲管運動」，逢星期五實施「無飲管日」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/news.modia.com.hk/2018/10/18/103141/大家樂明年全線分店棄膠飲管/amp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fnews.modia.com.hk%2F2018%2F10%2F18%2F103141%2F%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6%E6%A8%82%E6%98%8E%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%A8%E7%B7%9A%E5%88%86%E5%BA%97%E6%A3%84%E8%86%A0%E9%A3%B2%E7%AE%A1%2Famp%2F&d=pjepta7IDo9He3ZZvGfzZ3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=24bd4f58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/news.modia.com.hk/2018/10/18/103141/大家樂明年全線分店棄膠飲管/amp/</a>"},{"pid":"cf0ec9390724c0797114f6e1d5939cacffd19aed","tid":901971,"uid":68904,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T12:37:59.000Z","msg":"btw 我加左兩碟野食 所以多兩個盤"},{"pid":"5f8988e56a44cf2accded7e9163c0a071f0fbbee","tid":901971,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T12:39:12.000Z","msg":"咸能左 樓主好犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe7778495e65458127b794697155461ce0f0e08c","tid":901971,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T12:41:37.000Z","msg":"環保人士幾時出手救下魚苗<br />\n<br />\n[今次好波]【01獨家】香港邊界失守　內地漁民空群越境　違禁漁具「蛇籠」竭澤而漁 禍害海洋<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/893802\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/893802</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e3412225416f02fe9ee181b01a7518a7a12bb810","tid":901971,"uid":68904,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T12:43:41.000Z","msg":"sor 我唔係環保撚 淨係覺得佢淨係要走飲管好on9"},{"pid":"30b6394afeb239600dc15c555b6964457a886132","tid":901971,"uid":3501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T15:53:04.000Z","msg":"佢啲肥牛本身一packpack 用膠兜只會係開即棄嘅放落個兜度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}